It was so bright I ran away,

312
00:24:51,869 --> 00:24:55,369
いつだって弱くて
I was always so weak.

313
00:24:55,369 --> 00:24:58,269
あの日から
Unchanged since...

314
00:24:58,269 --> 00:24:59,569
変わらず
...that day.

315
00:25:00,081 --> 00:25:05,381
いつまでも変わらずに いられなかったこと
The fact that I couldn't stay the same forever

316
00:25:07,681 --> 00:25:09,581
悔しくて
It was so frustrating

317
00:25:09,581 --> 00:25:16,081
指を離す
that I let go of your fingers

318
00:25:17,881 --> 00:25:25,681
あの鳥はまだ うまく飛べないけど
That bird still can't fly well, but

319
00:25:25,681 --> 00:25:33,281
いつかは風を切って知る
someday it will know as it cuts through the wind

320
00:25:33,281 --> 00:25:41,281
