00:35:01,505 --> 00:35:06,705
開いた指の隙間から
Through the gaps between my open fingers...

361
00:35:06,705 --> 00:35:11,905
いつか手にしたままの
Still holding onto what I once gained...

362
00:35:11,905 --> 00:35:18,605
夢や憧れの種が
The seeds of my dreams and aspirations...

363
