明日へと芽吹出してる
they're sprouting towards tomorrow.

365
00:35:32,205 --> 00:35:37,105
逃げ出した昨日より
Rather than the yesterday I fled from,

366
00:35:37,105 --> 00:35:43,105
ぶつかりあった今日にこぼした涙
the tears I shed today after clashing...

367
00:35:43,105 --> 00:35:50,105
立ち止まった自分を連れて
Bringing along the self that came to a halt,

368
