Yes, thank you very much.

431
00:40:35,634 --> 00:40:37,517
あ、そうだ、ついでにこよりにね、
Oh, right, by the way, for Koyori...

432
00:40:37,634 --> 00:40:38,217
あ、はい。
Oh, yes.

